        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses GJR’s experiments on heliotropism in plants; views of Philippe van Tieghem and Julius von Wiesner. Describes his own experiments.</p> 
<p>Mentions his letter on vivisection [to Frithiof Holmgren, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">13115</hi>] in the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> [18 Apr 1881].</p> 
